<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:09:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列战事第 229 天：内塔尼亚胡表示以色列无意重新安置加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-229-netanyahu-says-israel-has-no-intention-of-resettling-gaza/0000018f-a0fc-dff6-a9af-eefee5b70000</link><description>挪威、爱尔兰和西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国，以色列召回特使进行磋商 ■ 以色列总检察长称，国际刑事法院检察官要求对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特发出逮捕令是“毫无根据的” ■ 斯莫特里奇表示，他不会转移为巴勒斯坦权力机构征收的税款直到另行通知为止” ■ 据报道，以色列和哈马斯之间的停战谈判因埃及秘密更改协议条款而破裂 ■ 这是战争开始 229 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-229-netanyahu-says-israel-has-no-intention-of-resettling-gaza/0000018f-a0fc-dff6-a9af-eefee5b70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长向承认巴勒斯坦的国家表示：“从河到海只有以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-to-nations-recognizing-palestine-only-israel-from-river-to-sea/0000018f-a0fc-d4c6-a5cf-f2fd3d0c0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，埃利·科恩部长强烈主张使用武力解救人质，包括全面入侵拉法</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-to-nations-recognizing-palestine-only-israel-from-river-to-sea/0000018f-a0fc-d4c6-a5cf-f2fd3d0c0000</guid></item><item><title>AG：国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的指控“毫无根据”；以色列考虑进行国家调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/ag-icc-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant-are-baseless-israel-mulls-state-inquiry/0000018f-a0c7-d60a-a9ef-f1ef24ea0000</link><description>总检察长表示，国际刑事法院无权对加沙战争期间可能犯下的战争罪进行调查；以色列对其在加沙的行动进行彻底、真正的调查可能会导致国际刑事法院暂停自己的调查</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/ag-icc-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant-are-baseless-israel-mulls-state-inquiry/0000018f-a0c7-d60a-a9ef-f1ef24ea0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡必须选择：无休止的加沙战争还是拜登的非凡协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-must-choose-endless-war-in-gaza-or-bidens-remarkable-deal/0000018f-96d7-dce9-a1cf-fed74a580000</link><description>拜登政府向内塔尼​​亚胡提出了一项可能击败哈马斯并确保沙特与以色列关系正常化的计划。但华盛顿对总理的无所作为越来越不耐烦，这有可能损害美国在该地区的信誉以及以色列的未来</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-must-choose-endless-war-in-gaza-or-bidens-remarkable-deal/0000018f-96d7-dce9-a1cf-fed74a580000</guid></item><item><title>挪威外长告诉《国土报》：承认巴勒斯坦是对内塔尼亚胡支持定居点政策的“反应”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/norway-fm-to-haaretz-recognizing-palestine-is-reaction-to-netanyahu-pro-settlement-policy/0000018f-a04c-da3b-a7ff-bbdd7f400000</link><description>埃斯彭·巴特·艾德表示，以色列政府对与巴勒斯坦人谈判没有兴趣，同时支持新的非法定居点，并补充说：“我们将继续与以色列保持朋友关系”</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 14:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/norway-fm-to-haaretz-recognizing-palestine-is-reaction-to-netanyahu-pro-settlement-policy/0000018f-a04c-da3b-a7ff-bbdd7f400000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛因“容忍”犹太人仇恨而被提起新诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/harvard-slapped-with-new-lawsuit-for-tolerating-jew-hatred/0000018f-9f7b-d264-a1bf-dfff36f00000</link><description>路易斯·D·布兰代斯人权中心在诉状中写道，“哈佛大学的信息很明确：只要针对以色列人和犹太人，歧视、骚扰或暴力都是可以接受的”。这是自10月7日以来常春藤盟校第二次因反犹太主义被起诉</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:38:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/harvard-slapped-with-new-lawsuit-for-tolerating-jew-hatred/0000018f-9f7b-d264-a1bf-dfff36f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长扩大允许返回撤离的约旦河西岸定居点的法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-chief-expands-law-allowing-return-to-evacuated-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-a019-d35f-a1df-ffd92cc20000</link><description>以色列国防部长加兰特下令取消 2005 年从西岸北部脱离接触的法律，并将其适用于三个定居点所在的地区。与此同时，以色列国防军中央司令部司令签署了一项禁止以色列人进入该地区的命令</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-chief-expands-law-allowing-return-to-evacuated-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-a019-d35f-a1df-ffd92cc20000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫寻求庇护者的孩子没有地位或未来，正在失去希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-tel-aviv-asylum-seekers-kids-are-losing-hope-this-is-the-result/0000018f-53dd-d348-a7bf-f7fda3680000</link><description>特拉维夫南部两个社区的居民同时参与了解决涉及移民和寻求庇护者社区青少年的反社会行为的活动。只有一个团体呼吁进行变革，这也将使非以色列居民受益</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-tel-aviv-asylum-seekers-kids-are-losing-hope-this-is-the-result/0000018f-53dd-d348-a7bf-f7fda3680000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时回避了有关与以色列媒体交谈的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dodges-questions-about-talking-to-israeli-media-in-cnn-interview/0000018f-9ff9-da3b-a7ff-9ffd1c950000</link><description>“他们没有告诉你的是，我已经与以色列媒体举行了 20 到 15 场新闻发布会。他们可以问任何他们想问的问题，他们也确实这么做了。”内塔尼亚胡对杰克·塔珀说道，塔珀专门询问的是采访而不是新闻发布会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:56:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dodges-questions-about-talking-to-israeli-media-in-cnn-interview/0000018f-9ff9-da3b-a7ff-9ffd1c950000</guid></item><item><title>世俗