s-have-left-the-church-is-fearful-for-the-communitys-future/0000018f-9f9b-d35f-a1df-dfdbeab70000</link><description>耶路撒冷宗主教自战争开始以来首次访问加沙的一座教堂，并会见了住在教堂内的家庭</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/over-half-of-gazas-christians-have-left-the-church-is-fearful-for-the-communitys-future/0000018f-9f9b-d35f-a1df-dfdbeab70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理本格维尔在访问圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺时谴责加沙援助和承认巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-rails-against-gaza-aid-recognition-of-palestine/0000018f-9f98-d6da-a1cf-ffba05300000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长本-格维尔表示，西班牙、挪威和爱尔兰承认巴勒斯坦国，这是对哈马斯的奖励</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:39:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-rails-against-gaza-aid-recognition-of-palestine/0000018f-9f98-d6da-a1cf-ffba05300000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭公布视频显示哈马斯恐怖分子绑架以色列女兵进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/hostage-families-to-release-video-of-hamas-terrorists-abducting-israeli-women-soldiers/0000018f-9f5c-d8f6-a3ef-9ffcdbf70000</link><description>10 月 7 日从纳哈尔奥兹基地被带走的军事观察员的父母决定公开这段经过剪辑和谴责的三分钟长视频。将于以色列时间下午 6 点发布</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/hostage-families-to-release-video-of-hamas-terrorists-abducting-israeli-women-soldiers/0000018f-9f5c-d8f6-a3ef-9ffcdbf70000</guid></item><item><title>据美国有线电视新闻网报道，埃及秘密修改协议条款后，以色列与哈马斯的人质协议破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/report-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-collapsed-after-egypt-secretly-altered-agreement/0000018f-9ed8-da3b-a7ff-9fdd011f0000</link><description>三名消息人士告诉美国有线电视新闻网，哈马斯接受的协议措辞与以色列和美国同意的草案不同。据他们称，中央情报局局长比尔·伯恩斯感到愤怒和尴尬，“差点就气炸了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 06:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/report-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-collapsed-after-egypt-secretly-altered-agreement/0000018f-9ed8-da3b-a7ff-9fdd011f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于他的极右翼联盟伙伴，内塔尼亚胡不会抓住美国与沙特的生命线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wont-grab-the-u-s-saudi-lifeline-because-of-his-far-right-coalition-partners/0000018f-9cc2-d35f-a1df-dfcb34ce0000</link><description>尽管美国关于以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间关系正常化的提议充满漏洞，但与利雅得达成的历史性协议可能是他唯一一张“免出狱”牌</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wont-grab-the-u-s-saudi-lifeline-because-of-his-far-right-coalition-partners/0000018f-9cc2-d35f-a1df-dfcb34ce0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属播放的镜头显示哈马斯恐怖分子绑架以色列女兵进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-not-planning-to-resettle-gaza-hamas-ouster-essential-for-day-after/0000018f-9df8-d376-a5bf-9ff9990d0000</link><description>五名以色列军事观察员的家人允许发布显示他们被哈马斯绑架的录像 ■ 以色列召回驻承认巴勒斯坦国的国家的大使 ■ 挪威、爱尔兰和西班牙将承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 巴勒斯坦被拘留者乘坐的军车碾压爆炸装置，身受重伤在西岸</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 01:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-not-planning-to-resettle-gaza-hamas-ouster-essential-for-day-after/0000018f-9df8-d376-a5bf-9ff9990d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长为内塔尼亚胡欺诈案辩护作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-testifies-in-support-of-netanyahus-defense-in-yedioth-fraud/0000018f-9ce2-d376-a5bf-9efba4390000</link><description>时任以色列议会内务委员会主席的亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 否认曾于 2014 年会见总理讨论推进以色列哈约姆法 (Yariv Levin)</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 22:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-testifies-in-support-of-netanyahus-defense-in-yedioth-fraud/0000018f-9ce2-d376-a5bf-9efba4390000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员担心以色列对巴勒斯坦国的抵制可能会阻碍沙特实现正常化的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-fear-israeli-pushback-on-palestinian-state-may-hinder-saudi-normalization/0000018f-9d11-d264-a1bf-df9705960000</link><description>美国高级外交官安东尼·布林肯在参议院外交关系委员会作证时概述了华盛顿在促成耶路撒冷和利雅得达成协议方面面临的主要障碍</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 21:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-fear-israeli-pushback-on-palestinian-state-may-hinder-saudi-normalization/0000018f-9d11-d264-a1bf-df9705960000</guid></item></channel></rss>